@Node "Usage_Edit_Multimedia" "Edit window: Multimedia files"

  On this page you can attach an unlimited number of multimedia files to
  each database entry.

  The buttons "New" and "Delete" should be self-explanatory. ;)
  Using the "Display" button or double-clicking on any of the entries
  will instruct CallMan to display the corresponding file using the
  multimedia viewer defined in the @{" preferences window " link "Prefs_CM_Page2"}

  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - "Hide entry?" :
    Activating this gadget will hide the entry and prevent it from being listed
    on the @{" main window's " link "Usage_Main"} list. Using the menu option
    @{" Show all entries " link "Usage_CMMenu" 67} you can temporarly make all the "hidden"
    entries reappear on the list.

