    Accept changes and return to the @{" main window " link "Usage_Main"}.

  - button "Cancel":
    Drop all changes and return to the @{" main window " link "Usage_Main"}.

@EndNode


@Node "Usage_Edit_Categories" "Edit window: categories"

  Here you can assign the current database entry to one or more of the
