@{b}CallMan 1.3 (23.02.1998):@{ub}
 - under certain circumstances TelephoneBill mode could refuse
   to calculate the phone costs; fixed
 - "save database" button was always selectable; fixed
 - "log call without dialling" without an entry selected would
   open an empty numbers window; fixed
 - analyzer would mess up names of unknown numbers; fixed
 - sometimes analyzer would mess up the display of numbers whose
   names are not present in the logfile but were found in the
   database; fixed
 - added "multimedia" section to database: user can now add any
