 - memory leak when attempting to open preferences window although
   preferences window is already open; fixed
 - title of "numbers window" displayed wrong name; fixed
 - after closing the edit window database list would lose focus on
   active entry; fixed
 - improved handling of defective CallMan logfiles (just in case ;)
 - whenever an entry was selected in the main window's database list,
