@Node "Ratesfiles" "Rates files"

The number of supplied rates files is quite low at the moment. :-)
Therefore I'm happy about each new rates file. I will include
each one (although without checking for accuracy) in the CallMan
archive as long as there isn't already a corresponding version
present.

Feel free to send me any corrections on already included files!

Please choose an appropriate filename and fill out the internal
description field.

